Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.40,0:00:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇，天氣真好，太陽好耀眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.72,0:00:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說起來\N我們好久沒有做日光浴了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.02,0:00:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.59,0:00:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乾淨的空氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.39,0:00:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拍打的浪花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.50,0:00:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.26,0:00:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然有點輕浮的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.97,0:00:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯，偶而無事偷閒也不賴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.07,0:00:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.54,0:00:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果沒有遇難的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.91,0:00:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.86,0:00:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,銀河天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.00,0:00:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼？為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.17,0:00:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危機，這下糟糕了\N緊張！緊張！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.84,0:01:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麻煩光線  BURU  BURU
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.67,0:01:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙大騷動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.08,0:01:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OK，胡鬧一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.04,0:01:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也沒關係，吃個飲茶\N好啊！好啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.68,0:01:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱著歡悅的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.82,0:01:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後一起向神明祈禱吧\NBANG  BANG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.09,0:01:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因果報應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.69,0:01:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每天都是冒險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.43,0:01:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一旦開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.36,0:01:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就讓它順其自然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.93,0:01:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有機關，沒有魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.24,0:01:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,孤注一擲的I.N.G.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.47,0:01:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無憂無慮的狂歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.08,0:01:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夢與希望的機關鎗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.75,0:01:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鎖定想要的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.18,0:01:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,BANG  BANG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.29,0:01:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跳舞吧，玩吧\NBRAVO！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.85,0:01:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坐上令人興奮的火箭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.56,0:02:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開闢天下無敵的成功之路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.57,0:02:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(特大碗生存定食)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.64,0:02:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我們偶爾才搭一次軍用機\N就遇到這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.01,0:02:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,運氣真不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.02,0:02:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也好，反正回去\N也是做一堆無聊的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.42,0:02:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我正想說是不是該放個假了呢\N我們就耐心等下去吧，薄荷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.19,0:02:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.80,0:02:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.27,0:02:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.20,0:02:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這該不會是最後的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.88,0:02:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸好是跟佛特在一起\N因為妳看起來蠻擅長野外求生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.12,0:02:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼什麼，求生還是年輕人厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.16,0:03:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們得去找食物\N還有，最好也要做個求救記號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.06,0:03:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是佛特\N像我就只會不安地無所適從
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.77,0:03:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才沒有這麼厲害啦\N(此時應由年輕人負責吧)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.47,0:03:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼會...我最崇拜堅強的佛特了\N(她難道沒有母愛嗎)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.04,0:03:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(真想和別人一起遇難)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.45,0:03:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人在那裡嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.62,0:03:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是可疑的人，我是警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.82,0:03:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警察？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.19,0:03:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是警察，是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.56,0:03:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼警察會在這種地方呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.50,0:03:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.56,0:03:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，這就說來話長了\N我是麥克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.80,0:03:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,半年前在押送犯人的時候\N飛機失事，便漂流到這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.47,0:03:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這故事聽起來不怎麼長啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.11,0:03:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該說是很短吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.31,0:03:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,半年？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.81,0:03:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這半年來，都沒有人來嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.18,0:03:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的，半年來都沒有人來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.12,0:03:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是不妙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.72,0:04:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.62,0:04:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我把周圍的廢物收集起來\N做了一個通訊器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.16,0:04:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大約從一個月前開始\N就一直送出SOS的求救信號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.86,0:04:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.36,0:04:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.10,0:04:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.20,0:04:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看，來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.57,0:04:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的是救援隊耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.91,0:04:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，開始囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.54,0:04:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發出SOS求救信號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.52,0:04:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個真的是SOS嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.19,0:04:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.19,0:04:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真奇怪，昨天好像也有\N一台飛機掉下來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.73,0:04:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.66,0:04:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個是電波干擾吧\N相當強烈的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.77,0:04:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.87,0:04:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是說...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.13,0:04:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.10,0:04:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.54,0:04:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特，這樣可以嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.05,0:05:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯，蠻多的嘛\N玩具之類的有沒有好好檢查呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.28,0:05:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為有些玩具附有通訊機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.59,0:05:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我當然有仔細檢查過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.79,0:05:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們一起合作發出求救信號嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.46,0:05:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你自己一個人努力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.09,0:05:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼這樣...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.09,0:05:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可以告訴妳很多\N關於島上的事喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.80,0:05:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.80,0:05:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳不需要作通訊器\N可以使用我的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.90,0:05:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種東西能用嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.07,0:05:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能在這裡認識也是種緣分啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.34,0:05:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.61,0:05:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有你，就不會有這段孽緣啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.92,0:05:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會不會有點過火呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.45,0:05:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別忘了是因為他\N我們才會遇到這倒楣事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.12,0:05:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡，為了這無聊事浪費體力\N啊...喉嚨好乾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.26,0:05:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我肚子餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.43,0:05:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.30,0:05:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有緊急用的乾糧喔\N很幸運，還有十年左右的存量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.44,0:05:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十年...？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.04,0:06:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀，麥克斯\N我也感覺這是難得的緣分呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.45,0:06:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這島上有麥克斯\N真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.08,0:06:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對吧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.65,0:06:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連軍用機也會失事\N佛特和薄荷真是倒楣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.13,0:06:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有點擔心\N搜索隊也還沒有任何消息傳來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.06,0:06:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事的，沒事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.10,0:06:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她們是天使隊中\N最不可能死的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.20,0:06:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在可能在某個地方逍遙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.57,0:06:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先不談那個，你們知道\N軍機掉落處被稱為惡魔海域嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.41,0:06:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惡魔...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.44,0:06:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,海域是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.25,0:06:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說那一帶很容易發生事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.78,0:06:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳言說...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.85,0:06:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,押送途中\N在那裡遇難而死的兇惡犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.19,0:06:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,變成了怨靈\N所以才會接連地發生事件呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.13,0:06:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開玩笑的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.53,0:07:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過在半年前真的有\N兇惡犯人在那附近遇難喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.60,0:07:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過若要說他是怨靈\N可能稍微缺少了一點震撼力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.68,0:07:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這感覺好久沒有過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.62,0:07:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯...這個嘛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.95,0:07:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個和這個接在一起\N這個和這個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.92,0:07:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.22,0:07:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,電話好像接通了耶\N雖然是通訊器...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.46,0:07:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特真是天才
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.36,0:07:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這時候不管是什麼了，快接吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.83,0:07:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恭喜你\N你是第一萬個打電話來的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.60,0:07:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們要送你一個\N夏天無人島之旅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.11,0:07:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸運的你\N現在的心情覺得如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.08,0:07:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是令人火大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.08,0:07:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次怎麼樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.52,0:07:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，這裡是電話購物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.72,0:07:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說出來妳可能不相信\N我現在在無人島...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.09,0:08:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下再問您住址\N首先請說想訂的商品編號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.49,0:08:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是要訂貨的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.73,0:08:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼下次也等待您的來電
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.07,0:08:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝您打電話來今子的房間\N今天會認識哪位朋友呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.84,0:08:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您撥的電話目前可能\N收不到訊號或是電源沒開...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.18,0:08:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喔...佛特的煩惱是？\N嗯...別吵，別來煩我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.12,0:08:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通訊好像真的沒辦法接通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.73,0:08:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唉，沒想到我的人生\N要在這種地方結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.60,0:08:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好想談個美好的戀愛再死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.87,0:08:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞不好會和麥克斯\N談個美好的戀愛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.24,0:08:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會吧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.07,0:08:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戀愛這種事會造成身體的錯覺\N回過神後才發現已陷進去了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.85,0:08:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在放棄還太早了\N再來使用這個通訊器看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.48,0:09:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果打到了葬儀社就好笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.95,0:09:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，它只有在發出干擾電波時\N才最有效用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.49,0:09:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以干擾電波一直讓飛機失事墜落\N這樣就能讓人發現這裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.86,0:09:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.26,0:09:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳能去問問麥克斯\N看看有沒有多餘的電池好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.87,0:09:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.37,0:09:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂！麥克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.51,0:09:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不在嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.01,0:09:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然是被困在這裡\N生活倒是挺不錯的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.54,0:09:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麥克斯，跟你要水喝囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.08,0:09:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這...這是什麼東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.51,0:09:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在押送犯人時遇難...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.79,0:09:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道那傢伙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.01,0:10:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麥克斯，你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.15,0:10:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好高興喔\N你們來到這島上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.45,0:10:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一個人正悶得發慌呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.46,0:10:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.13,0:10:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特怎麼去那麼久呢\N我來稍微試試看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.44,0:10:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會讓妳逃走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.98,0:10:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.45,0:10:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？這是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.49,0:10:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在受到不明電波干擾\N而墜落中，無法操控
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.79,0:10:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.16,0:10:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.74,0:11:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不曉得為什麼\N不過總之得救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.44,0:11:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼這樣...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.18,0:11:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本來想和佛特獨處\N讓妳來鞭打我的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.15,0:11:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不對？佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.82,0:11:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這白癡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.32,0:11:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.19,0:11:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偶而這樣也不錯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.36,0:11:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.00,0:11:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到所謂的兇惡犯人\N原來只是兇惡的SM迷啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.77,0:11:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過跟佛特搞不好蠻配的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.04,0:11:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.27,0:11:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.74,0:11:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的救援隊\N什麼時候才會來呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.11,0:11:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.25,0:11:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.68,0:11:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下個菜單是  「外送比薩」\N其實我家被討債的人追趕著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.85,0:11:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果每天都得這麼辛苦\N那我乾脆和妹妹兩人一起...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.26,0:11:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.42,0:11:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗚...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.23,0:11:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該是在說外送比薩的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.83,0:11:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對，是在說外送比薩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.58,0:12:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,滿天的星辰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.25,0:12:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像是打翻水瓶似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.59,0:12:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,躺在新月下的吊床
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.46,0:12:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作了夢之後，變得想見你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.10,0:12:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,側耳傾聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.24,0:12:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看，不是聽見了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.28,0:12:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令人興奮的天線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.25,0:12:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要讓它睡著  NO  NO
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.39,0:13:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,處女座的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.33,0:13:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向牡羊座的你發出\N急電，急電
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.40,0:13:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乘著飛馬的翅膀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.47,0:13:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前去迎接你
